{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1e2e785777","title":"刘少奇给湖南省长王首道的信","origin":"一九五七年九月，人民出版社资料室《批判资料：中国赫鲁晓夫刘少奇反革命修正主义言论集》（1958．6—1967．7）（387）","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dd2493cf31","index":0,"year":1950,"month":12,"day":24,"articleId":"1e2e785777"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9986567b57","name":"刘少奇"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fca4de7f60","type":"title","text":"刘少奇给湖南省长王首道的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1e2e785777"},{"id":"bc9b38f7f3","type":"authors","text":"刘少奇","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1e2e785777"},{"id":"ba1f21671f","type":"subtitle","text":"[王首道：中共湖南省委副书记，湖南省人民政府主席]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1e2e785777"},{"id":"2943bcb480","type":"appellation","text":"首道同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1e2e785777"},{"id":"0946398010","type":"paragraph","text":"我的七哥刘作衡由北京回家，路经长沙，请你招待数日，他即自行回家。据他说乡下征粮有一些是过重的，交不起，这恐不完全是地主们的叫嚣，有加以考虑之必要。又我六哥家中因无劳动力，他儿子出来参加工作十余年，不能顾家，现家中老小数口要吃，亦交不起粮，不知有无办法减少。又我七哥有一个孙子，想到长沙学校读书，不知是否有免费的学校给他入学，如有，望给以帮助，麻烦之处，望予原谅。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1e2e785777"},{"id":"93e924c864","type":"paragraph","text":"此致","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1e2e785777"},{"id":"4443cb42a0","type":"appellation","text":"敬礼","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1e2e785777"},{"id":"51d2326cd9","type":"paragraph","text":" 刘少奇十二月二十四日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1e2e785777"}],"page":{"id":"0cf268e86c","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1e2e785777","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}